question: Maharashtra government decided to rename the Mumbai Central station as to which of the following name?
option1: Savitribai Phule Mumbai Central railway station
option2: Bal Gangadhar Tilak Mumbai Central railway station
option3: B. R. Ambedkar Mumbai Central railway station
option4: Nana Shankarsheth Mumbai Central railway station
answer: Nana Shankarsheth Mumbai Central railway station
explanation: Maharashtra government decided to rename the Mumbai Central station as Nana Shankarsheth Mumbai Central railway station. Jagannath Shankarseth was an Indian philanthropist and educationalist. He was born in Mumbai.
